\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"The associated pod 'redis-cart-0' running on 'aiops-k8s-08' demonstrates increased latency 'rrt_max' and 'rrt', likely due to node resource constraints.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max increased from 2167.0 ms to 3416.0 ms (change_ratio: 0.4474). rrt increased with a change_ratio of 0.017.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n总结：分析表明故障由 Node `aiops-k8s-08` 的内存压力引起，导致运行在该 Node 上的 Pod 如 `redis-cart-0` 性能下降。这是初步扫描结果，还需后续深度分析以确认相关的服务调用链异常状态。"}
